Package: matrixFunctions
Title: Collection of Functions for Matrix Differentiation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Thanakorn",
           family = "Nitithumbundit",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "t.nitithumbundit@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0971-2111"))
Description: A collection of functions for matrix differentiation. Numeric matrix 
    derivatives are implemented using Richardson's extrapolation method, and
    computational improvements to some matrix functions in matrixcalc package.
